channel.description:
What's up? The name's WackyModder84. Idk if ya heard of me, but you may like what I have to offer if u meet the following conditions:

- Are u a fan of "Mobile Suit Gundam"?
- Are u a fan of Mecha Anime IN GENERAL?
- Do u have a shitty PC but wanna play actual GOOD GAMES still?
- Do u want Good Advice on PCs, Gaming, etc... ?

If so, then ypu couldn't have chosen a better Youtube Channel to come to. =)

I've been a fan of Gundam for 16 Years now and possess amazing knowledge of the whole entire saga.
I reach out my hand 2 those who have Shitty PCs & show them an ARSENAL of amazing Low-Spec PC Games for them 2 play safely on their Crap PCs.
And I also reveal 2 the world AMAZING Mecha Games that not many ppl know about & that the world SHOULD know about.
To me: Subscribers Numbers & View Numbers don't mean a damn thing in determining if a channel is of Great Quality.
I don't say "Like, Fav, & Sub 4 More!" HELL NO! I let the people decide for themselves on that.

Hope you like it here! =D
